WEBVTT

00:02:52.440 --> 00:02:53.480
My Lord, bad news.

00:02:53.880 --> 00:02:54.520
What is it?

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:56.320
Someone has requested a night trial for the three suspects.

00:02:56.960 --> 00:02:57.600
Who?

00:02:57.600 --> 00:02:58.320
It is I.

00:03:01.720 --> 00:03:03.960
I am Lu Shijie, the top lawyer of Shuntian Prefecture.

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:05.200
Commissioned by the Tang Clan.

00:03:05.360 --> 00:03:06.520
Here are the appeal documents.

00:03:06.880 --> 00:03:08.160
According to the Great Ming Code of Interrogation and Judgment...

00:03:08.160 --> 00:03:09.440
Section 28, Article 29...

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:10.120
And Article 16.

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:11.240
I am filing a complaint against the Grand Court of Justice.

00:03:11.360 --> 00:03:12.920
For, in the absence of sufficient evidence...

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.440
Arresting innocent civilians.

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:16.800
Namely Tang Xi, Yuan Ran, and Wu Qiangu.

00:03:26.240 --> 00:03:27.400
Thank you, Lawyer Lu.

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:28.640
For saving us from this misery.

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:30.320
My old bones...

00:03:30.600 --> 00:03:32.600
Can handle a little grievance, it doesn't matter.

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:34.640
But my poor sister Yuan Ran...

00:03:34.920 --> 00:03:36.200
She has always been frail.

00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:37.240
She was perfectly fine...

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:38.840
But the shock has triggered her hysteria.

00:03:39.240 --> 00:03:39.960
And the crazy girl...

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:42.040
Was injured by the Vice Minister of the Dali Temple.

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:43.360
Her internal injuries haven't healed...

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:44.520
And now she's been frightened again.

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:45.840
Now...

00:03:46.480 --> 00:03:48.160
She is suffering here!

00:03:48.920 --> 00:03:50.360
Public morals are declining day by day!

00:03:50.800 --> 00:03:51.800
Morality is in ruin!

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:52.920
The dignified Grand Court of Justice...

00:03:52.920 --> 00:03:55.080
Would actually treat the old, weak, women, and children this way!

00:03:56.480 --> 00:03:57.080
Lord Pei.

00:03:57.280 --> 00:03:58.640
According to the Great Ming Code of Interrogation and Judgment...

00:03:58.640 --> 00:04:00.040
Section 28, Article 29...

00:04:00.040 --> 00:04:01.440
Article 4, Article 10, and Article 15.

00:04:01.520 --> 00:04:03.920
I want to add a charge against the Grand Court for torturing the old and young.

00:04:03.960 --> 00:04:04.840
For mental abuse.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:06.280
Attempting to use severe torture and cruel laws...

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:07.600
To force a confession.

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:10.040
According to the laws of the Great Ming...

00:04:10.200 --> 00:04:11.880
Your additional accountability...

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:13.200
Is not inappropriate.

00:04:14.040 --> 00:04:15.440
However, this case...

00:04:15.920 --> 00:04:19.840
Involves the Eastern Depot and the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:21.920
This...

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:26.720
Lawyer Lu.

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:28.040
These three people...

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:29.520
Although arrested by the Grand Court of Justice...

00:04:29.960 --> 00:04:31.640
Were arrested at the request of the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

00:04:32.760 --> 00:04:35.240
Let alone arrest, interrogation, or private torture...

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:37.760
Even if we were to execute them on the spot...

00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:40.280
It falls within the scope of our authority.

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:41.800
This additional accountability...

00:04:42.640 --> 00:04:43.640
Is invalid.

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:47.360
I was presumptuous.

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:49.720
Commander Shen has the authority of the Imperial Prison.

00:04:50.080 --> 00:04:51.920
But judgment must follow a trial.

00:04:52.200 --> 00:04:54.000
You would never place yourself above Imperial power...

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:55.160
And use unjust, false, and wrong cases...

00:04:55.360 --> 00:04:56.840
To repay His Majesty's trust.

00:04:57.200 --> 00:04:57.640
After all...

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:59.000
Since the founding of our dynasty...

00:04:59.200 --> 00:05:01.120
We have governed the realm by law.

00:05:01.640 --> 00:05:02.320
That...

00:05:03.400 --> 00:05:04.560
Is naturally so.

00:05:05.760 --> 00:05:07.760
To prevent others from speculating on the actions of the Depots and Guards...

00:05:07.760 --> 00:05:08.880
And to show our innocence...

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:10.720
The murder case of the Superintendent...

00:05:11.040 --> 00:05:12.640
Was handed over to the Grand Court of Justice.

00:05:13.080 --> 00:05:13.680
We...

00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:16.040
Are merely assisting.

00:05:18.760 --> 00:05:20.960
The Grand Court of Justice, in accordance with the Great Ming Code,

00:05:21.200 --> 00:05:22.800
shall enforce the law impartially,

00:05:23.080 --> 00:05:24.400
without any negligence.

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:27.440
Now,

00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:30.120
regarding the issues raised by Lawyer Lu Shijie,

00:05:30.280 --> 00:05:31.400
we shall proceed with the inquiry.

00:05:32.280 --> 00:05:33.160
Suspect Tang Xi.

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:34.400
Do you all know

00:05:34.640 --> 00:05:37.080
why you were arrested and brought to the Grand Court of Justice today?

00:05:37.680 --> 00:05:38.520
In reply, My Lord,

00:05:38.960 --> 00:05:40.000
this commoner does not know.

00:05:40.440 --> 00:05:42.800
Now, I invite Vice Minister Zhang Yi

00:05:42.920 --> 00:05:44.800
to question the suspects.

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:46.560
Yes, My Lord.

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:49.120
Suspect Wu Qiangu,

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:50.680
suspected of using hallucinogenic potions

00:05:51.040 --> 00:05:52.320
to disrupt order at the execution ground,

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:53.760
causing a commotion among the people,

00:05:54.400 --> 00:05:55.680
and leading to the murder of the Commander.

00:05:56.760 --> 00:05:57.640
Suspect Yuan Ran,

00:05:57.960 --> 00:05:59.960
suspected of using puppets

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:01.920
to physically attack the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

00:06:02.200 --> 00:06:03.040
Suspect Tang Xi,

00:06:03.720 --> 00:06:05.440
suspected of disguising as the Snow Maiden Dou E,

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:08.160
assisting the criminal Li Chenyang in escaping the execution ground.

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:10.440
The three of you publicly mocked last night's robbery,

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:13.400
openly provoking the authority of the Grand Court of Justice and the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

00:06:13.840 --> 00:06:14.600
Wu Qiangu,

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:15.800
Yuan Ran,

00:06:16.200 --> 00:06:16.760
Tang Xi,

00:06:17.080 --> 00:06:20.080
do you three admit to the crimes alleged by Vice Minister Zhang?

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:23.840
He's lying through his teeth.

00:06:24.040 --> 00:06:25.320
This is a frame-up.

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:27.320
I am just a humble woman.

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:29.160
My Lord, please do not wrong an innocent person.

00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:31.080
This commoner believes the Great Ming Code

00:06:31.080 --> 00:06:33.480
will grant this commoner a fair and just verdict,

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:35.200
to restore my innocence.

00:06:35.640 --> 00:06:37.160
The three refuse to plead guilty.

00:06:37.640 --> 00:06:38.520
Now,

00:06:38.600 --> 00:06:40.680
Lawyer, please defend the three.

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:43.200
Thank you, Lord Pei.

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:45.240
Our dynasty relies on evidence as the basis,

00:06:45.440 --> 00:06:46.720
and the Great Ming Code as the criterion.

00:06:46.920 --> 00:06:47.480
I dare to ask,

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:49.280
Vice Minister of the Dali Temple, Lord Zhang Yi,

00:06:49.320 --> 00:06:50.920
you suspect Wu Qiangu of using illusion potions

00:06:51.320 --> 00:06:52.800
to disrupt the execution ground order.

00:06:53.320 --> 00:06:55.040
Is there any evidence to prove this?

00:06:55.400 --> 00:06:55.880
Danqing.

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:57.280
Present the evidence.

00:06:58.560 --> 00:06:59.600
This is what I collected:

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:00.480
willow catkins from the execution ground last night,

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:01.800
and the plum branches

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.480
that Wu Qiangu gifted to the people.

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.120
The agents in these two items,

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:05.800
when mixed together,

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:07.560
cause intense hallucinations

00:07:07.960 --> 00:07:09.440
and lead one to attack and harm others.

00:07:09.560 --> 00:07:11.720
The evidence provided by Lord Zhang seems sound.

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:14.240
I also witnessed the events yesterday.

00:07:14.480 --> 00:07:15.840
Hearing the Lords explain it today,

00:07:16.040 --> 00:07:17.320
it suddenly makes sense.

00:07:18.520 --> 00:07:19.360
Wu Qiangu,

00:07:20.520 --> 00:07:21.280
these plum blossoms,

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:23.080
are they what you gifted to the people?

00:07:23.320 --> 00:07:23.840
In reply, My Lord,

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:24.920
these plum blossoms

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.000
are indeed mine.

00:07:26.320 --> 00:07:27.680
But the potion within them

00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:29.320
is to stimulate the blooming of the plum blossoms,

00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:30.360
and is harmless.

00:07:30.680 --> 00:07:32.520
It allows those who smell the plum blossoms

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:33.960
to feel refreshed and happy.

00:07:34.280 --> 00:07:36.520
Then are these willow catkins from your home?

00:07:36.880 --> 00:07:39.280
My home has no willow trees, so where would catkins come from?

00:07:39.720 --> 00:07:40.720
If you insist on forcing this on me...

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:42.240
Willow catkins fly all over the capital.

00:07:42.640 --> 00:07:44.040
Then are all the people of the capital

00:07:44.040 --> 00:07:45.640
the owners of the willow catkins?

00:07:46.680 --> 00:07:47.640
Everyone has heard.

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:49.720
Wu Qiangu admits to gifting plum blossoms to the people,

00:07:49.880 --> 00:07:51.360
but does not admit to the matter of the willow catkins.

00:07:51.560 --> 00:07:53.280
Just because of a harmless potion in the plum blossoms,

00:07:53.400 --> 00:07:55.520
to frame Wu Qiangu, an alchemist,

00:07:55.720 --> 00:07:56.160
is perhaps

00:07:56.800 --> 00:07:57.720
a bit too rash, isn't it?

00:07:57.840 --> 00:07:58.720
But within these willow catkins,

00:07:58.720 --> 00:08:00.480
there is indeed a potion brewed by Wu Qiangu.

00:08:00.520 --> 00:08:01.160
Lord Zhang,

00:08:01.560 --> 00:08:03.040
has the Grand Court of Justice found

00:08:03.040 --> 00:08:03.080
the potion formula handwritten by Wu Qiangu?

00:08:03.080 --> 00:08:05.480
The potion formula handwritten by Wu Qiangu?

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:07.360
Or did this formula come from a witness?

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:08.120
Or perhaps

00:08:08.400 --> 00:08:10.120
receipts for purchasing the potion ingredients?

00:08:14.640 --> 00:08:15.720
There is currently no valid evidence.

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:16.560
Then,

00:08:16.960 --> 00:08:18.560
you cannot convict based on this.

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:19.760
Without evidence or proof,

00:08:19.760 --> 00:08:21.320
it is a frame-up, a false accusation.

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:22.840
It is Vice Minister Zhang's investigation

00:08:23.080 --> 00:08:24.320
that is not thorough enough.

00:08:25.520 --> 00:08:26.280
Lord Pei,

00:08:26.440 --> 00:08:27.520
Commander Shen,

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:29.160
the Grand Court of Justice must not wrong

00:08:29.160 --> 00:08:30.760
such a wandering performer,

00:08:30.880 --> 00:08:34.360
and chill the hearts of all the people in the capital.

00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:40.480
I only ask, my lords,

00:08:40.840 --> 00:08:44.120
for fairness and justice, nothing more.

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:46.120
The number one lawyer of Shuntian Prefecture

00:08:46.360 --> 00:08:47.960
lives up to his reputation.

00:08:48.400 --> 00:08:49.160
Lawyer Lu,

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.520
I will make my own judgment.

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:51.960
Continue your questioning,

00:08:54.480 --> 00:08:55.200
Vice Minister Zhang.

00:08:58.440 --> 00:09:00.040
As for the evidence of Yuan Ran's crimes,

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:03.000
please ask the Grand Court of Justice coroner

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:03.560
to come forward and state the facts.

00:09:05.800 --> 00:09:06.600
Reporting, my lord.

00:09:07.080 --> 00:09:09.800
From the bodies of the deceased Embroidered Uniform Guards,

00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:12.400
the fatal wounds were caused by falling into an illusion

00:09:12.680 --> 00:09:15.000
and hacking each other with Embroidered Spring Swords.

00:09:15.440 --> 00:09:17.040
However, the sword wounds on the bodies

00:09:17.160 --> 00:09:20.160
differ from those made by the Embroidered Spring Swords.

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:20.600
Therefore,

00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:22.360
I deduce that

00:09:22.680 --> 00:09:23.880
it was Yuan Ran utilizing

00:09:23.880 --> 00:09:25.600
puppets dressed as evil spirits

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:27.840
to mix in with the Guards and confuse them,

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:29.400
making the Embroidered Uniform Guards doubt

00:09:29.400 --> 00:09:30.840
the reality of what they were seeing.

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:31.640
In this world,

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:33.400
how could anyone control

00:09:33.880 --> 00:09:36.240
a puppet the same size as a human

00:09:36.560 --> 00:09:37.640
and use it to harm people?

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:39.920
Among the many commoner witnesses present last night,

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:40.800
who

00:09:40.800 --> 00:09:42.480
can prove that it was Yuan Ran controlling

00:09:42.480 --> 00:09:43.560
these so-called puppets

00:09:43.720 --> 00:09:44.680
to harm people?

00:09:44.680 --> 00:09:45.560
Or perhaps,

00:09:45.560 --> 00:09:47.280
if the puppets that caused harm were found,

00:09:47.520 --> 00:09:48.440
let this humble one

00:09:48.680 --> 00:09:49.440
take a look.

00:09:49.760 --> 00:09:51.040
Last night, the people were all under an illusion.

00:09:51.560 --> 00:09:53.080
In the chaos, everyone was only concerned with escaping.

00:09:53.240 --> 00:09:53.720
No one saw

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:55.120
how she manipulated the puppets.

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:56.520
As for where the puppets are now,

00:09:56.800 --> 00:09:58.200
that is a question for the criminal Yuan Ran.

00:09:58.440 --> 00:10:00.760
My puppets are just wooden dolls for opera.

00:10:00.960 --> 00:10:03.320
How could they possibly harm anyone?

00:10:03.800 --> 00:10:04.760
My lord,

00:10:04.760 --> 00:10:06.600
you overestimate me.

00:10:07.560 --> 00:10:08.360
So,

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:09.480
simply because

00:10:09.560 --> 00:10:11.640
a puppeteer was found at the crime scene,

00:10:11.840 --> 00:10:12.800
you attribute the puppets

00:10:12.920 --> 00:10:14.480
to the puppeteer based on speculation.

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:17.200
Lord Zhang, relying on your own guesses and imagination

00:10:17.400 --> 00:10:19.880
to convict a woman from the Western Regions,

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:22.680
really makes one suspect you of regional discrimination.

00:10:22.760 --> 00:10:23.760
How dare you, Lu Shijie!

00:10:24.080 --> 00:10:24.920
Do not fabricate accusations

00:10:24.920 --> 00:10:25.640
and use underhanded tactics.

00:10:25.640 --> 00:10:26.480
I wouldn't dare.

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:28.320
If Your Lordship wants to convict Yuan Ran,

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:29.760
you can issue a reward notice

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:31.320
to find witnesses among the commoners from last night.

00:10:31.520 --> 00:10:33.680
Engaging in a war of words with me in this court now

00:10:33.800 --> 00:10:35.240
before the Great Ming laws

00:10:35.880 --> 00:10:36.760
is meaningless.

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:38.440
Zhang Yi,

00:10:40.880 --> 00:10:43.680
how could you handle this case so carelessly?

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:48.200
This matter was my oversight.

00:10:48.640 --> 00:10:49.640
Focusing all my energy on

00:10:49.640 --> 00:10:51.080
the pursuit of Li Chenyang

00:10:51.280 --> 00:10:53.320
meant the Grand Court of Justice could only achieve this much.

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:55.720
My Lord,

00:10:56.400 --> 00:10:57.440
blame me for the lack of evidence.

00:10:58.120 --> 00:10:59.440
But Tang Xi hijacking Li Chenyang

00:10:59.680 --> 00:11:00.840
was tracked personally by me,

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:01.920
and I exchanged blows with her.

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:03.320
The martial arts and hidden weapons she used

00:11:03.520 --> 00:11:04.240
were all from the Tang Clan.

00:11:05.520 --> 00:11:06.160
Lord Zhang,

00:11:06.960 --> 00:11:08.520
the Great Ming Penal Code clearly states

00:11:08.840 --> 00:11:11.240
the principles of pursuit, sentencing, and classification.

00:11:11.360 --> 00:11:12.120
I know that.

00:11:12.440 --> 00:11:14.200
The Great Ming Code's regulations on arrests state

00:11:14.320 --> 00:11:16.400
that arresting a suspect requires a squad of more than one,

00:11:16.520 --> 00:11:17.360
acting together to make the arrest,

00:11:17.640 --> 00:11:19.000
to avoid false accusations

00:11:19.920 --> 00:11:20.480
or misjudgments.

00:11:21.920 --> 00:11:22.360
What?

00:11:22.640 --> 00:11:23.440
Are you trying to teach me my job?

00:11:23.720 --> 00:11:24.560
I wouldn't dare.

00:11:25.000 --> 00:11:26.440
I am just kindly reminding you, My Lord,

00:11:26.680 --> 00:11:28.600
so that in this year's Censorate-hosted

00:11:28.600 --> 00:11:29.760
Great Ming Law examination,

00:11:30.560 --> 00:11:31.640
you do not miss the easy points.

00:11:31.880 --> 00:11:32.240
You...

00:11:32.760 --> 00:11:33.920
There is something you all may not know.

00:11:34.160 --> 00:11:35.240
The Tang Clan Young Master, Tang Xi,

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:37.040
has studied the Great Ming laws since childhood.

00:11:37.160 --> 00:11:38.160
Naturally, she would not commit

00:11:38.160 --> 00:11:40.200
the stupidity of knowingly breaking the law and doubling the crime.

00:11:40.320 --> 00:11:41.080
Furthermore,

00:11:41.520 --> 00:11:43.640
if Lord Zhang had truly encountered the Tang Clan Young Master,

00:11:44.040 --> 00:11:44.840
I fear that by now,

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:46.640
you would be lying dead in the mortuary.

00:11:47.600 --> 00:11:48.200
Young Master Tang,

00:11:48.360 --> 00:11:50.160
why not present the sword you brought to the capital

00:11:50.440 --> 00:11:51.240
to everyone here

00:11:51.400 --> 00:11:52.160
for a closer look?

00:11:52.200 --> 00:11:54.440
It was taken by the Grand Court of Justice officials before the interrogation.

00:11:55.280 --> 00:11:57.040
Present Tang Xi's sword.

00:12:05.360 --> 00:12:06.240
This is

00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:11.440
This is the Sword of Authority

00:12:11.440 --> 00:12:13.520
bestowed upon my ancestor by Emperor Taizu of Ming

00:12:16.680 --> 00:12:19.080
If I had held this sword while fighting Lord Zhang last night

00:12:19.520 --> 00:12:20.840
I would not have shown any mercy

00:12:21.360 --> 00:12:22.720
Those who can execute first and report later

00:12:23.160 --> 00:12:24.400
are not limited to the Depots and Guards

00:12:25.400 --> 00:12:26.760
However, this Sword of Authority

00:12:26.760 --> 00:12:28.360
cannot prove my innocence

00:12:28.640 --> 00:12:30.200
I was merely showing off a little

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:33.080
I have three Iron Certificates of Pardon at home

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:34.520
They are simply too heavy

00:12:35.080 --> 00:12:36.080
or I would have brought them along as well

00:12:36.960 --> 00:12:38.440
The suspects today all came prepared

00:12:38.680 --> 00:12:40.760
I truly underestimated the Tang Clan Young Master's skills

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:42.960
The Tang Clan helped Emperor Taizu achieve his great cause

00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:44.440
For a century, they sought no fame or fortune

00:12:44.520 --> 00:12:45.480
yet they forged good karma far and wide

00:12:46.080 --> 00:12:47.000
Zhang Yi

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:48.680
Your involvement in Li Chenyang's case

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:49.960
could it be you have ulterior motives

00:12:49.960 --> 00:12:52.120
Although solving the case is urgent

00:12:52.600 --> 00:12:54.120
your impetuousness

00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:56.240
has been counterproductive

00:12:57.080 --> 00:12:58.640
Punish yourself with thirty strokes

00:12:58.640 --> 00:12:59.800
as a warning to others

00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:02.800
Considering you are handling a major case

00:13:03.160 --> 00:13:04.600
it is reduced to ten strokes

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:08.360
I shall take your teachings to heart, My Lord

00:13:10.520 --> 00:13:11.400
I

00:13:11.920 --> 00:13:14.160
Grand Judge Pei Yuandong, pronounce judgment

00:13:14.840 --> 00:13:18.360
Wu Qiangu, Tang Xi, Yuan Ran

00:13:18.920 --> 00:13:19.960
are acquitted and released

00:13:20.480 --> 00:13:21.360
But the three of you

00:13:21.680 --> 00:13:23.840
are not yet fully cleared of suspicion

00:13:24.320 --> 00:13:25.920
During the three-day lockdown of the capital

00:13:26.320 --> 00:13:28.040
you must not leave without permission

00:13:29.400 --> 00:13:30.360
To prove our innocence

00:13:30.600 --> 00:13:31.400
we naturally obey

00:13:31.680 --> 00:13:32.480
your arrangements, My Lord

00:13:34.680 --> 00:13:35.320
Court is adjourned

00:13:42.280 --> 00:13:42.800
Lord Zhang

00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:44.280
Vice Minister Zhang

00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:47.440
Today you attacked me in the street without cause

00:13:47.800 --> 00:13:49.400
nearly costing me my life

00:13:49.920 --> 00:13:51.080
and ruining my reputation

00:13:51.720 --> 00:13:52.600
About this matter

00:13:53.360 --> 00:13:54.840
what should be done

00:13:57.440 --> 00:13:57.960
What

00:13:58.680 --> 00:13:59.560
Are you playing the rogue with me

00:14:00.240 --> 00:14:01.280
Your martial arts are clearly superior

00:14:01.280 --> 00:14:02.280
Why didn't you fight back

00:14:02.360 --> 00:14:03.240
If I fought back

00:14:03.800 --> 00:14:04.720
wouldn't I be charged with

00:14:04.720 --> 00:14:06.480
the heavy crime of harming a fourth-rank court official

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:08.600
and be detained by you at the Grand Court of Justice

00:14:09.560 --> 00:14:10.520
Or perhaps

00:14:10.720 --> 00:14:11.960
we should ask Lawyer Lu again

00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:13.800
to walk us through the process

00:14:15.720 --> 00:14:16.560
So what do you want

00:14:19.080 --> 00:14:19.560
What do I want

00:14:19.880 --> 00:14:22.200
Money for the veil and medical expenses

00:14:22.560 --> 00:14:23.000
You

00:14:29.560 --> 00:14:30.160
Take it all

00:14:30.320 --> 00:14:30.880
Let's go

00:14:37.560 --> 00:14:39.000
You wicked girl

00:14:40.080 --> 00:14:40.800
You're petty

00:14:40.840 --> 00:14:41.760
but extremely damaging

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:42.880
This time

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:44.720
I actually sympathize with Lord Zhang a bit

00:14:50.640 --> 00:14:51.080
Enough

00:14:51.440 --> 00:14:52.520
I've figured it out

00:14:52.800 --> 00:14:53.360
You all

00:14:53.560 --> 00:14:54.960
are martial arts experts

00:14:54.960 --> 00:14:56.160
and Jianghu people accustomed to legal procedures

00:14:57.120 --> 00:14:58.440
This trip to the Grand Court of Justice

00:14:59.000 --> 00:15:00.240
was a first for me

00:15:00.640 --> 00:15:01.880
Mr. Lu is a wise man

00:15:02.920 --> 00:15:04.200
He doesn't state the truth explicitly

00:15:04.320 --> 00:15:05.440
but he has the ability to guide others

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:06.840
to a different kind of truth

00:15:08.080 --> 00:15:09.000
However

00:15:09.600 --> 00:15:10.520
this Lord Zhang

00:15:11.440 --> 00:15:13.440
doesn't seem to look at you very kindly

00:15:16.240 --> 00:15:17.880
Tang Xi bringing the Sword of Authority to the capital

00:15:17.920 --> 00:15:18.600
is definitely not simple

00:15:19.400 --> 00:15:21.400
We must not let the three of them leave the capital

00:15:21.840 --> 00:15:22.480
It is four people

00:15:24.280 --> 00:15:25.160
On the night of the crime

00:15:25.440 --> 00:15:26.280
I saw Lu Shijie

00:15:27.200 --> 00:15:28.400
I thought he was just an idler

00:15:28.400 --> 00:15:29.200
coming to watch the commotion

00:15:30.080 --> 00:15:30.720
Now it seems

00:15:32.040 --> 00:15:33.400
Lu Shijie, in this case

00:15:33.760 --> 00:15:35.080
also played a key role

00:15:35.920 --> 00:15:36.840
Come

00:15:37.080 --> 00:15:42.160
Everyone gets one

00:15:43.320 --> 00:15:45.120
Everyone

00:16:04.640 --> 00:16:05.800
Between Zhang Yi and me

00:16:06.480 --> 00:16:08.840
our grudges go far beyond what happened today

00:16:09.160 --> 00:16:10.880
Wipe that gloomy look off your face

00:16:12.200 --> 00:16:13.160
Do not forget

00:16:13.640 --> 00:16:15.000
who we are going to meet right now

00:16:35.200 --> 00:16:38.320
This is Blossom Pavilion, famed above all in the capital

00:16:38.800 --> 00:16:40.640
Though it is a land of wine and courtesans

00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:43.960
it holds a charm half real, half dreamlike

00:16:44.880 --> 00:16:45.720
The girls here

00:16:45.720 --> 00:16:46.920
are skilled in zither, chess, calligraphy, and painting

00:16:46.960 --> 00:16:48.320
that is nothing out of the ordinary

00:16:48.640 --> 00:16:49.520
Their charms are endless

00:16:49.600 --> 00:16:50.400
each with her own unique grace

00:16:50.600 --> 00:16:53.120
Scholars and poets all find someone to their liking

00:16:53.680 --> 00:16:54.440
When you start to cherish them

00:16:54.960 --> 00:16:56.560
you fear your own tenderness

00:16:56.760 --> 00:16:57.960
might only bring trouble to the beauty

00:16:58.680 --> 00:16:59.680
Let me see

00:16:59.960 --> 00:17:00.960
which girl

00:17:01.400 --> 00:17:02.520
can truly catch my eye

00:17:06.440 --> 00:17:07.440
Eyes like flowing water

00:17:08.040 --> 00:17:09.200
bright and captivating

00:17:10.520 --> 00:17:13.120
Pity I am just a common soul of the mortal world

00:18:13.200 --> 00:18:14.080
I have found her

00:18:15.480 --> 00:18:17.600
a true earthly enchantress

00:18:52.600 --> 00:18:53.720
That is her

00:18:54.440 --> 00:18:57.040
Eyes like stars attending the moon

00:18:57.640 --> 00:18:58.920
At the tips of her brows and eyes

00:18:59.160 --> 00:19:01.400
a charm she simply cannot hide

00:19:03.080 --> 00:19:04.720
If I were a young man

00:19:05.200 --> 00:19:07.040
I would feast and revel with her every night

00:19:07.400 --> 00:19:08.560
until dawn

00:19:09.160 --> 00:19:10.160
Young master, you have fine taste

00:19:10.920 --> 00:19:12.600
This is the one who recommended us here

00:19:12.600 --> 00:19:13.960
Lady Hua Shuoyue

00:19:14.680 --> 00:19:15.400
Win her over

00:19:15.680 --> 00:19:16.880
and the whole Blossom Pavilion

00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:18.480
will be yours

00:19:20.120 --> 00:19:20.800
How vulgar

00:19:21.520 --> 00:19:23.600
If you only covet Blossom Pavilion’s intel and worth

00:19:23.600 --> 00:19:24.440
when you look at this beauty

00:19:25.800 --> 00:19:27.520
you will never be worthy of her

00:19:46.920 --> 00:19:49.480
Lady Hua cares not for gold or jewels

00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:51.480
nor does she fancy ancient books

00:19:52.440 --> 00:19:54.680
She treats silks and satins like children

00:19:55.120 --> 00:19:58.360
I know you most love plum blossoms in deep winter

00:19:58.680 --> 00:20:00.320
I specially had the craftsmen of the imperial garden

00:20:00.600 --> 00:20:01.720
cultivate these spring plum blossoms

00:20:01.920 --> 00:20:02.880
Whatever you desire

00:20:03.520 --> 00:20:04.480
I can make it happen

00:20:05.600 --> 00:20:07.200
Snow in the fourth month

00:20:08.880 --> 00:20:10.480
plum blossoms in bloom

00:20:12.800 --> 00:20:14.920
are still lifeless things tainted by common hands

00:20:16.560 --> 00:20:17.800
bereft of spirit

00:20:19.360 --> 00:20:22.120
Only when plum blossoms bloom on Lady Hua’s brow

00:20:22.360 --> 00:20:23.040
do they become truly alive

00:20:23.240 --> 00:20:24.240
filling the garden with spring

00:20:25.840 --> 00:20:26.680
As for me

00:20:27.840 --> 00:20:30.080
there is one thing I have always wanted

00:20:30.480 --> 00:20:32.720
If it could win a single smile from a beauty

00:20:33.280 --> 00:20:34.320
I would go to heaven or into the depths of earth

00:20:34.560 --> 00:20:35.320
and think nothing of it

00:20:36.880 --> 00:20:38.040
Then I want

00:20:39.280 --> 00:20:40.440
birds that dive into the sea

00:20:41.360 --> 00:20:42.960
and fish that swim through the clouds

00:20:43.800 --> 00:20:45.400
dreams that touch the hidden workings of fate

00:20:46.120 --> 00:20:48.120
and know the will of heaven

00:21:04.360 --> 00:21:05.520
You are truly a remarkable soul

00:21:06.040 --> 00:21:06.920
Rarely do women

00:21:07.720 --> 00:21:08.800
manage, like you

00:21:09.120 --> 00:21:10.280
to be so unrestrained and at ease

00:21:10.600 --> 00:21:13.040
The Tang Clan young master is just as the rumors say

00:21:13.560 --> 00:21:15.560
a mad, unfathomable figure

00:21:16.840 --> 00:21:18.840
Your employer has been waiting for quite some time

00:21:19.640 --> 00:21:20.680
Please follow me

00:21:34.240 --> 00:21:36.360
So we truly are here to meet the one behind the scenes

00:22:11.760 --> 00:22:13.480
You are clearly from the martial world,

00:22:14.000 --> 00:22:15.920
yet you played the Eastern Depot and the Embroidered Uniform Guard

00:22:16.080 --> 00:22:17.640
like puppets in your hands.

00:22:18.560 --> 00:22:20.920
Your skills are truly impressive.

00:22:22.840 --> 00:22:23.640
I am

00:22:24.000 --> 00:22:24.720
Tang Xi.

00:22:25.760 --> 00:22:26.640
Wu Qiangu.

00:22:28.440 --> 00:22:29.200
Yuan Ran.

00:22:29.520 --> 00:22:30.320
Lu Shijie.

00:22:31.200 --> 00:22:33.560
We pay our respects to the Eunuch Lord of the Western Depot.

00:22:35.560 --> 00:22:36.840
We are not in the palace,

00:22:37.440 --> 00:22:39.280
so there is no need for such tedious formalities.

00:22:40.040 --> 00:22:41.560
You will be more at ease this way.

00:22:43.160 --> 00:22:44.760
Thank you for your consideration, Lord Wang.

00:22:45.720 --> 00:22:48.160
Then we will make ourselves at home.

00:22:49.240 --> 00:22:51.000
The Young Master of the Tang Clan is intelligent

00:22:51.200 --> 00:22:52.120
and possesses exceptional courage.

00:22:52.920 --> 00:22:54.200
According to Shuoyue,

00:22:54.480 --> 00:22:55.840
the kidnapping of Li Chenyang

00:22:55.840 --> 00:22:57.480
was planned single-handedly by you.

00:22:58.520 --> 00:23:00.960
It truly gave me quite a surprise.

00:23:01.280 --> 00:23:03.880
It was merely a little entertainment.

00:23:04.560 --> 00:23:06.120
Since it caught the Eunuch Lord's eye,

00:23:06.960 --> 00:23:09.040
I assume we have passed your test.

00:23:12.240 --> 00:23:13.800
You are certainly not humble.

00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:17.000
If I were humble,

00:23:17.560 --> 00:23:18.960
I would be insincere.

00:23:22.200 --> 00:23:23.080
As for the test,

00:23:23.280 --> 00:23:25.000
I simply wanted to gauge your abilities.

00:23:26.240 --> 00:23:27.520
If I have offended you,

00:23:28.080 --> 00:23:29.080
I hope you will forgive me.

00:23:29.800 --> 00:23:30.680
No offense taken.

00:23:30.720 --> 00:23:31.600
You are Wang Zhi.

00:23:31.640 --> 00:23:32.440
We are just here to get

00:23:32.440 --> 00:23:34.160
the reward that belongs to us.

00:23:38.160 --> 00:23:38.720
Please.

00:23:50.600 --> 00:23:51.720
Ninjutsu.

00:23:52.400 --> 00:23:53.800
Wang Zhi's running dog.

00:23:54.000 --> 00:23:54.960
Enlighten me.

00:24:05.360 --> 00:24:05.680
Let's go

00:24:15.480 --> 00:24:16.760
I can understand your eagerness to claim credit

00:24:17.640 --> 00:24:19.040
But to do something as stupid as tailing,

00:24:19.040 --> 00:24:20.080
you actually managed to do it

00:24:20.320 --> 00:24:21.360
Just how much do you want to prove yourself,

00:24:21.360 --> 00:24:22.400
that you have the ability to screw everything up?

00:24:22.640 --> 00:24:24.080
I already know the mastermind behind the robbery

00:24:24.920 --> 00:24:26.400
It's better than you, who has a detective's brain,

00:24:27.000 --> 00:24:28.400
but can only grin like a fool while working

00:24:29.360 --> 00:24:29.520
I...

00:24:30.880 --> 00:24:31.840
I shouldn't have saved you

00:24:41.240 --> 00:24:42.600
Shen Youzhi was taken away by Zhang Yi

00:24:42.920 --> 00:24:44.080
I fear the Eastern Depot already knows

00:24:44.200 --> 00:24:45.280
that you are involved in this robbery

00:24:46.000 --> 00:24:48.120
I just want those old fools to know

00:24:48.440 --> 00:24:49.440
who it is recently

00:24:49.760 --> 00:24:51.040
that is rattling the Eastern Depot

00:24:51.640 --> 00:24:53.880
Know your own identity and status

00:24:56.360 --> 00:24:56.880
You may leave

00:24:57.400 --> 00:24:57.920
Yes

00:25:02.480 --> 00:25:03.800
I want to completely root out

00:25:04.040 --> 00:25:05.640
the Eastern Depot's power in the court

00:25:06.320 --> 00:25:07.000
Therefore,

00:25:07.640 --> 00:25:09.000
I need everyone's assistance

00:25:09.680 --> 00:25:11.040
What needs to be done next

00:25:11.360 --> 00:25:13.760
is not just cleaning up the Li Chenyang matter,

00:25:13.760 --> 00:25:14.640
it's not that simple anymore

00:25:17.720 --> 00:25:18.440
Lord Wang,

00:25:18.800 --> 00:25:19.520
you flatter us

00:25:20.240 --> 00:25:22.720
The Western Depot's power is now above the Eastern Depot's

00:25:23.240 --> 00:25:24.200
Moreover,

00:25:24.680 --> 00:25:26.560
you should know better than us

00:25:26.720 --> 00:25:28.680
the background of Eunuch Lord Shang Hua of the Eastern Depot

00:25:30.160 --> 00:25:31.400
Why would you need

00:25:31.880 --> 00:25:33.640
jianghu folks like us

00:25:34.040 --> 00:25:35.680
to provide such trivial assistance?

00:25:37.880 --> 00:25:39.520
Now you're being modest again

00:25:40.760 --> 00:25:41.880
The Eastern Depot's power

00:25:41.880 --> 00:25:43.400
is deeply entrenched in the court

00:25:43.680 --> 00:25:44.680
To root it out

00:25:45.160 --> 00:25:46.080
is no easy task

00:25:46.520 --> 00:25:47.680
But if the Emperor

00:25:47.920 --> 00:25:49.280
loses faith in the Eastern Depot,

00:25:49.560 --> 00:25:50.440
then it would be different

00:25:51.040 --> 00:25:52.960
So I need to find the Eastern Depot's

00:25:52.960 --> 00:25:55.040
true location for collecting secret reports

00:25:55.320 --> 00:25:57.200
And obtain all the

00:25:57.200 --> 00:25:58.520
ledgers and materials detrimental to the Eastern Depot

00:25:58.840 --> 00:25:59.840
And these tasks

00:26:01.080 --> 00:26:02.880
can only be done by you

00:26:03.440 --> 00:26:04.880
Lord Wang is looking for a group of

00:26:04.880 --> 00:26:06.720
people who, even if the plan fails,

00:26:07.040 --> 00:26:09.040
won't expose him...

00:26:09.840 --> 00:26:10.600
scapegoats

00:26:12.040 --> 00:26:13.760
You've calculated this well, my Lord

00:26:16.080 --> 00:26:17.480
This is an interesting matter

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:20.320
But it requires your full cooperation

00:26:20.480 --> 00:26:21.320
Between us and you,

00:26:21.320 --> 00:26:23.160
aside from the binding of mutual interests,

00:26:23.840 --> 00:26:24.920
there remains only

00:26:24.920 --> 00:26:25.880
the trust that you won't

00:26:25.880 --> 00:26:27.040
kill us to silence us

00:26:31.520 --> 00:26:32.560
The Young Master of the Tang Clan

00:26:33.680 --> 00:26:35.040
sees things clearly indeed

00:26:35.600 --> 00:26:37.720
I like working with smart people

00:26:38.360 --> 00:26:39.960
Help me get one step closer to

00:26:39.960 --> 00:26:41.360
Eunuch Lord Shang Hua of the Eastern Depot,

00:26:41.920 --> 00:26:43.880
so I can find out the latest news

00:26:44.640 --> 00:26:47.080
If the Eastern Depot's true secret intelligence site

00:26:47.400 --> 00:26:48.680
was so easy to find,

00:26:50.120 --> 00:26:50.880
it wouldn't require you

00:26:50.880 --> 00:26:52.640
to worry so much about it

00:26:55.840 --> 00:26:56.480
Simple

00:26:57.360 --> 00:26:59.400
The old fool has been ill recently

00:27:01.200 --> 00:27:02.480
It's time to pay him a visit

00:27:08.760 --> 00:27:09.600
Is Lord Shen injured?

00:27:10.440 --> 00:27:11.720
Should we go to the Grand Court of Justice to treat it first?

00:27:12.600 --> 00:27:13.520
You don't need to worry about my business

00:27:13.800 --> 00:27:15.000
You should worry about yourself first

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:15.720
Lord Zhang,

00:27:16.400 --> 00:27:18.920
leave Commander Shen to us to arrange

00:27:19.160 --> 00:27:21.000
You should go back and rest early

00:27:30.920 --> 00:27:32.160
It seems this Lord Shen

00:27:32.400 --> 00:27:33.880
is quite a formidable character

00:27:56.840 --> 00:27:57.360
Lin Feng

00:27:59.720 --> 00:28:00.520
I will kill you

00:28:01.200 --> 00:28:01.600
Lin Feng

00:28:02.520 --> 00:28:04.040
You shameless eunuch thief

00:28:04.440 --> 00:28:05.800
You destroyed our lives

00:28:06.240 --> 00:28:08.160
The hatred of taking my wife, Shuoyue

00:28:08.360 --> 00:28:09.640
Is absolutely irreconcilable

00:28:11.440 --> 00:28:12.040
Lin Feng

00:28:16.680 --> 00:28:17.600
You had a nightmare

00:28:23.040 --> 00:28:25.280
Hearing about this Zhang Yi character last night

00:28:26.840 --> 00:28:29.000
Reminded me of unpleasant past events

00:28:29.320 --> 00:28:31.240
You need not explain to me

00:28:31.720 --> 00:28:33.280
You are beneath only one

00:28:33.640 --> 00:28:35.400
And above ten thousand, Eunuch Lord

00:28:36.920 --> 00:28:38.320
Even if you took my life

00:28:39.720 --> 00:28:40.800
Who would dare say a word?

00:28:42.120 --> 00:28:43.440
You have a sharp tongue

00:28:45.480 --> 00:28:46.040
Attendants

00:28:48.880 --> 00:28:49.360
Here

00:28:49.760 --> 00:28:50.760
Go to the Eastern Depot

00:28:51.280 --> 00:28:52.920
Notify Grand Judge Pei Yuandong

00:28:53.160 --> 00:28:54.480
And Vice Minister of the Dali Temple Zhang Yi

00:28:54.720 --> 00:28:55.920
To go there and wait together

00:28:56.600 --> 00:28:56.920
Yes

00:29:29.840 --> 00:29:30.680
Youzhi

00:29:31.400 --> 00:29:32.440
What matter

00:29:32.920 --> 00:29:34.520
Nearly made you lose your composure?

00:29:36.760 --> 00:29:37.720
Nothing escapes your eyes

00:29:38.920 --> 00:29:40.640
Western Depot Commander Wang Zhi

00:29:41.760 --> 00:29:43.400
Has arrived at the Eastern Depot hall to demand answers

00:29:49.280 --> 00:29:49.920
Attendants

00:29:50.760 --> 00:29:51.520
Change my clothes

00:30:25.040 --> 00:30:26.000
Hold it tight.

00:30:26.480 --> 00:30:28.280
This is Consort Wan's new favorite.

00:30:28.600 --> 00:30:30.200
If anything goes wrong,

00:30:31.000 --> 00:30:32.760
not only will your head roll,

00:30:33.520 --> 00:30:35.200
but perhaps the Eastern Depot's

00:30:35.200 --> 00:30:36.640
Grand Secretary Eunuch position

00:30:37.960 --> 00:30:39.240
will also change hands.

00:30:39.760 --> 00:30:41.040
Eunuch Lord Wang,

00:30:41.800 --> 00:30:44.480
whether my Grand Secretary Eunuch position changes

00:30:45.080 --> 00:30:46.840
is for His Majesty to decide.

00:30:48.040 --> 00:30:49.000
Could it be that

00:30:49.400 --> 00:30:52.120
you can now make decisions for His Majesty?

00:30:54.520 --> 00:30:56.760
It seems the newly appointed Commander Song

00:30:56.960 --> 00:30:59.040
wants to test my Western Depot's capabilities.

00:31:01.400 --> 00:31:02.080
Very well.

00:31:02.760 --> 00:31:04.680
Tomorrow I will petition His Majesty

00:31:05.080 --> 00:31:06.640
to satisfy your request.

00:31:14.000 --> 00:31:15.520
Recently, regarding how the commoners

00:31:15.640 --> 00:31:17.240
are discussing the Grand Court of Justice

00:31:17.240 --> 00:31:18.040
and the Eastern Depot's

00:31:18.200 --> 00:31:18.960
handling of cases,

00:31:19.680 --> 00:31:20.640
Master Pei,

00:31:20.920 --> 00:31:21.920
have you heard?

00:31:22.440 --> 00:31:24.600
I have heard a little.

00:31:26.000 --> 00:31:27.560
The Grand Court arrested a suspect,

00:31:27.880 --> 00:31:29.760
only to release him as innocent in the end.

00:31:30.000 --> 00:31:31.640
Making the Grand Court and Eastern Depot

00:31:32.000 --> 00:31:34.080
a laughingstock among the people.

00:31:34.680 --> 00:31:35.600
For this matter,

00:31:36.120 --> 00:31:37.840
someone must take responsibility,

00:31:38.600 --> 00:31:40.040
lest others in the court

00:31:41.000 --> 00:31:42.480
follow suit.

00:31:43.800 --> 00:31:45.680
I am truly ashamed.

00:31:46.040 --> 00:31:47.800
To express my apology,

00:31:48.040 --> 00:31:49.440
tomorrow I will ask His Majesty

00:31:49.560 --> 00:31:52.280
for permission to resign as Grand Judge

00:31:52.640 --> 00:31:53.960
and return to my hometown.

00:31:55.240 --> 00:31:58.000
That Master Pei has such awareness

00:31:58.560 --> 00:32:00.960
is truly a model for the court.

00:32:02.000 --> 00:32:03.120
Eunuch Lord Wang,

00:32:03.480 --> 00:32:04.960
the fault does not lie with Master Pei.

00:32:05.240 --> 00:32:06.680
It was my eagerness to solve the case

00:32:06.760 --> 00:32:07.520
and acting on my own initiative

00:32:07.720 --> 00:32:08.680
that caused the current situation

00:32:08.960 --> 00:32:10.560
for the Grand Court and Eastern Depot.

00:32:12.360 --> 00:32:12.800
Zhang Yi!

00:32:12.840 --> 00:32:14.360
I am willing to bear all responsibility.

00:32:15.440 --> 00:32:16.400
Zhang Yi,

00:32:18.880 --> 00:32:20.600
you're one who dares to take charge.

00:32:20.920 --> 00:32:22.120
Since the foolish act

00:32:22.400 --> 00:32:23.800
of arresting a suspect without evidence

00:32:23.840 --> 00:32:25.480
was single-handedly orchestrated

00:32:25.480 --> 00:32:26.320
by Vice Minister Zhang,

00:32:26.520 --> 00:32:26.800
then...

00:32:26.800 --> 00:32:27.800
"Laws are

00:32:28.160 --> 00:32:29.240
the tools of governance,

00:32:30.720 --> 00:32:33.600
not the source of order and chaos."

00:32:34.760 --> 00:32:37.200
Our founding Emperor valued the rule of law

00:32:37.280 --> 00:32:39.960
and compiled the thirty volumes of the Great Ming Code.

00:32:40.240 --> 00:32:41.920
Which volume mentions

00:32:42.560 --> 00:32:45.200
that ineffective work by Grand Court officials

00:32:45.480 --> 00:32:46.960
leading to public criticism

00:32:47.600 --> 00:32:48.760
is a punishable offense?

00:32:50.840 --> 00:32:51.400
Godfather,

00:32:51.680 --> 00:32:52.440
you have misunderstood.

00:32:52.880 --> 00:32:53.800
You were ill

00:32:53.800 --> 00:32:55.000
and recuperating.

00:32:55.440 --> 00:32:57.320
It was these useless people

00:32:57.440 --> 00:32:59.800
who let Feng Hai, Li Chenyang's execution supervisor, suffer.

00:33:00.080 --> 00:33:01.680
The criminal official Li Chenyang escaped

00:33:02.120 --> 00:33:03.680
and has not been heard from since.

00:33:04.640 --> 00:33:06.560
Each and every one of these events

00:33:07.240 --> 00:33:09.360
is a great humiliation for the Eastern Depot.

00:33:10.160 --> 00:33:10.840
For this matter,

00:33:11.720 --> 00:33:13.520
someone must take responsibility,

00:33:13.960 --> 00:33:15.400
lest others in the court

00:33:16.160 --> 00:33:17.520
follow suit.

00:33:30.600 --> 00:33:31.760
You may all sit down.

00:33:41.480 --> 00:33:43.520
Eunuch Lord Wang, you flatter me.

00:33:43.960 --> 00:33:46.080
I am now old and frail.

00:33:46.600 --> 00:33:48.880
All I have left is my age.

00:33:50.440 --> 00:33:51.720
How am I qualified...

00:33:52.040 --> 00:33:54.000
To still be called Godfather by you?

00:33:55.600 --> 00:33:58.000
As for recent events...

00:33:59.920 --> 00:34:02.480
One should not rejoice over joyless matters.

00:34:02.880 --> 00:34:05.040
Nor anger over things unworthy of rage.

00:34:06.800 --> 00:34:08.040
I have seen through it all.

00:34:08.400 --> 00:34:10.520
You need not take it to heart either.

00:34:12.520 --> 00:34:14.120
It is you, Godfather, who has taken it to heart.

00:34:14.960 --> 00:34:17.040
Though I am Eunuch Lord of the Western Depot...

00:34:17.360 --> 00:34:19.360
I have never dared to forget...

00:34:19.720 --> 00:34:22.440
The kindness of your mentorship and promotion, Godfather.

00:34:22.800 --> 00:34:25.040
I always wish for everything to go your way...

00:34:25.760 --> 00:34:27.560
So you may enjoy your old age in peace.

00:34:30.240 --> 00:34:31.760
Treat the real as empty.

00:34:32.280 --> 00:34:33.760
Treat the empty as real.

00:34:36.200 --> 00:34:38.000
You and I treat each other with sincerity.

00:34:38.080 --> 00:34:39.160
Yet sincerity is met with rifts.

00:34:40.400 --> 00:34:41.120
As for...

00:34:41.720 --> 00:34:44.880
Eunuch Lord Wang valuing my cultivation of character...

00:34:45.320 --> 00:34:47.160
Then you should not let minor details...

00:34:47.160 --> 00:34:48.200
Harm the greater integrity.

00:34:49.880 --> 00:34:51.200
Instead of seeking profit for me...

00:34:51.720 --> 00:34:52.640
It would be better...

00:34:54.480 --> 00:34:55.320
To seek peace.

00:34:57.520 --> 00:34:58.480
Right now...

00:34:58.760 --> 00:35:00.160
I ask for very little.

00:35:03.000 --> 00:35:03.680
Eunuch Lord Wang.

00:35:04.120 --> 00:35:07.080
Early this morning, in the name of the Western Depot...

00:35:07.400 --> 00:35:09.200
You came to the Eastern Depot to condemn us.

00:35:10.520 --> 00:35:11.760
In what way...

00:35:12.240 --> 00:35:14.680
Is this showing filial respect to your Godfather?

00:35:16.040 --> 00:35:16.880
Filial respect...

00:35:17.280 --> 00:35:18.680
Is naturally not expressed in words.

00:35:20.560 --> 00:35:23.040
Bring up the gift I prepared for Godfather.

00:35:32.440 --> 00:35:33.080
Godfather.

00:35:33.480 --> 00:35:35.200
Knowing you love calligraphy and painting...

00:35:35.640 --> 00:35:36.800
A few days ago...

00:35:37.040 --> 00:35:39.120
I specifically asked His Majesty for a reward.

00:35:39.880 --> 00:35:41.800
A painting by His Majesty's own hand.

00:35:43.160 --> 00:35:44.280
The famous Song Dynasty Prime Minister...

00:35:44.800 --> 00:35:46.400
Wang Anshi's "On the River".

00:35:47.320 --> 00:35:48.200
Today...

00:35:49.040 --> 00:35:50.440
I present it to you with respect.

00:36:02.120 --> 00:36:03.200
Please, Eunuch Lord Wang...

00:36:03.600 --> 00:36:05.000
Thank His Majesty for me.

00:36:05.520 --> 00:36:08.840
I will certainly hang this painting carefully in my room.

00:36:12.160 --> 00:36:15.160
Take the "Memorial on Deploying the Troops" I copied last night...

00:36:15.240 --> 00:36:16.480
And present it to His Majesty as a return gift.

00:36:19.360 --> 00:36:20.240
In this way...

00:36:20.480 --> 00:36:21.920
I imagine Godfather's mood...

00:36:22.320 --> 00:36:23.760
Will surely be much smoother.

00:36:27.160 --> 00:36:28.200
As for you all...

00:36:29.920 --> 00:36:32.080
If the Eastern Depot doesn't care about losing face...

00:36:32.360 --> 00:36:33.920
The Western Depot will no longer pursue it either.

00:36:34.880 --> 00:36:35.520
But remember.

00:36:36.440 --> 00:36:37.160
Matters...

00:36:37.840 --> 00:36:39.440
Must eventually have a conclusion.

00:37:03.800 --> 00:37:05.280
Useless trash.

00:37:06.240 --> 00:37:08.120
Can't even take care of a cat properly.

00:37:09.440 --> 00:37:11.760
How can you take care of my Godfather?

00:37:13.600 --> 00:37:14.440
Little Xi.

00:37:17.720 --> 00:37:18.400
I am here.

00:37:25.040 --> 00:37:26.560
You stay at the Eastern Depot for a day.

00:37:26.800 --> 00:37:29.320
Teach the people serving the Eunuch Lord properly.

00:37:30.120 --> 00:37:31.280
Show them...

00:37:32.440 --> 00:37:36.200
How you take care of Consort Wan's pets.

00:37:37.440 --> 00:37:38.000
Yes.

00:37:42.400 --> 00:37:43.160
Commander Wang.

00:37:43.560 --> 00:37:45.400
His Majesty and Consort Wan are overjoyed.

00:37:46.040 --> 00:37:47.200
They summon you to the palace immediately.

00:37:56.200 --> 00:37:56.840
Godfather.

00:37:57.320 --> 00:37:59.560
I will return to the palace first to serve His Majesty.

00:38:00.160 --> 00:38:03.440
I wish you longevity and health.

00:38:04.720 --> 00:38:06.600
Thank you for your trouble, Lord Wang.